            <p class="hero-subtitle">
              Engineering student at MITAOE with a passion for practical solutions, software development, and building refined digital experiences.
            </p>
            <a class="button-primary" href="#projects">View My Projects</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-visual">
            <div class="hero-card">
              <h3 style="margin-top:0">Quick Info</h3>
              <p style="color:var(--muted); line-height:1.6; font-size: 0.9rem;">
                <strong>PRN:</strong> 202501100150<br>
                <strong>Batch:</strong> SE2 S22<br>
                I am focused on creating dependable software solutions with thoughtful logic.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="about">
          <div class="section-header">
            <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Education and enthusiasm.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about">
            <p style="color:var(--muted); line-height:1.75">
              I am an engineering student at MIT Academy of Engineering (MITAOE). My focus is on creating dependable solutions with clear design and thoughtful logic. I approach every project with curiosity and a drive to learn.
            </p>
            <div class="about-card">
              <h3 style="margin-top:0">Current Profile</h3>
              <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--muted)">Software Engineering Student at MITAOE</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="skills">
          <div class="section-header">
            <h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Core technologies and programming skills.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-grid">
            <div class="skill-card"><h4>HTML</h4><p style="color:var(--muted)">Web structure</p></div>
            <div class="skill-card"><h4>CSS</h4><p style="color:var(--muted)">Visual design</p></div>
            <div class="skill-card"><h4>Python</h4><p style="color:var(--muted)">Automation & Logic</p></div>
            <div class="skill-card"><h4>C++</h4><p style="color:var(--muted)">Performance</p></div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="projects">
          <div class="section-header">
